title: GET_THRUSTER_THROTTLE
content:
0x94E24C96// GetThrusterThrottle
float GET_THRUSTER_THROTTLE(Vehicle jetpack);Parameters:jetpack: The jetpack to check.Returns: Returns a value representing the main throttle of the jetpack. The values range from 0.0 (no throttle) to 1.0 (full throttle)
codeBlocks:
local ped = PlayerPedId()
local vehicle = GetVehiclePedIsIn(ped, false)
-- Example usage for GET_THRUSTER_THROTTLE
GetThrusterThrottle(vehicle)
